{"tid":805814,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟揸walkie旁白條友企喺邊？","createTime":"2018-09-04T07:00:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T07:19:29.000Z","uid":2104,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3138e9c1f1326f1a6f518182a3790bb5d96da089","tid":805814,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:00:14.000Z","msg":"明明條山路又長又多灣 企喺山頂應該睇唔晒所有路段<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但佢又可以清楚描述到每個灣位每段路每架車嘅車速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就連個車手想搵位出 出路出到佢都睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n車手嘅跑法佢都可以講到出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁佢究竟喺邊個位可以睇得咁清楚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連架車一邊轆落咗坑渠入灣都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果佢係後面揸車 咁佢咪揸得好快？<br />\n又要跟住啲車又唔快過車手又唔可以甩仲唔可以入鏡仲要旁述埋 <br />\n咁佢應該先係神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n極速傳說仲誇張<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n由觀塘海皮一路追到入清水灣 都冇甩過...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n究竟知walkie旁述人喺邊先可以咁清楚場賽事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/04/145940_26bd1ec1c005f2f5cb77ed08b5e7f2e3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F04%2F145940_26bd1ec1c005f2f5cb77ed08b5e7f2e3.png&h=a86be199&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c45ec871044dad0cabc6cd1994c8b8d6b76853f1","tid":805814,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T07:10:28.000Z","msg":"收風再轉述"},{"pid":"e82bc1c529c2f2f869ea5b691c6112de99ddfd6a","tid":805814,"uid":6530,"like":0,"dislik